      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you set an action on an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsmenutoolbaritem"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " control item, the user invokes the action when clicking on the item through pressing and holding to display the menu. If you set an action on the item and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsmenutoolbaritem/3237192-showsindicator"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the system displays the indicator as a separate segment so the user can invoke the menu with a click on that segment. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you don’t set an action on the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsmenutoolbaritem"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", a simple click invokes the menu, and the indicator is purely decorative."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
